  "remarks": "\nFormer aide to the President of the Russian Federation. He was an organiser of the process in Crimea by which local Crimean communities were mobilised to stage actions undermining the Ukrainian authorities in Crimea. Remains active in supporting separatist actions or policies. The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
